    {
        "content": "<p>Hello, </p>\n<p>I'm trying to compile Asahi Linux (on Asahi Linux) downloaded from official github repo. Reason - I want to learn how to build a simple Linux kernel module in Rust<br>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/AsahiLinux/linux\">https://github.com/AsahiLinux/linux</a></p>\n<p>steps:</p>\n<p><code>cd ~/asahi-linux</code><br>\n<code>make clean &amp;&amp; make mrproper</code><br>\n<code>make defconfig</code></p>\n<p>applying my custom config rules for rust kernel development, disabling these rules:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"s\">\"CONFIG_DEBUG_INFO_BTF\"</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"s\">\"CONFIG_BPF\"</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"s\">\"CONFIG_BPF_SYSCALL\"</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"s\">\"CONFIG_BPF_JIT\"</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"s\">\"CONFIG_BPF_STREAM_PARSER\"</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"s\">\"CONFIG_BPF_PRELOAD\"</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"s\">\"CONFIG_BPF_LSM\"</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"s\">\"CONFIG_BPF_LSM_MAC\"</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"s\">\"CONFIG_BPF_JIT_ALWAYS_ON\"</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"s\">\"CONFIG_INIT_STACK_ALL_ZERO\"</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"s\">\"CONFIG_STACKPROTECTOR\"</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"s\">\"CONFIG_MODULE_SIG\"</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"s\">\"CONFIG_MODULE_SIG_ALL\"</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"s\">\"CONFIG_MODVERSIONS\"</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"s\">\"CONFIG_MODULE_SIG_FORCE\"</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"s\">\"CONFIG_MODULE_COMPRESS\"</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"s\">\"CONFIG_MODULE_COMPRESS_GZIP\"</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"s\">\"CONFIG_MODULE_COMPRESS_XZ\"</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"s\">\"CONFIG_MODULE_COMPRESS_ZSTD\"</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p><code>make -j$(nproc)</code></p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"o\">..</span><span class=\"p\">.</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">CC</span><span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"n\">drivers</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">scsi</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">scsi_sysfs</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">o</span>\n<span class=\"n\">error</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"n\">E0050</span><span class=\"p\">]:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">method</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"err\">`</span><span class=\"n\">init</span><span class=\"err\">`</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">has</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">parameter</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">but</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">the</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">declaration</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">in</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">trait</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"err\">`</span><span class=\"n\">kernel</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">Module</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">init</span><span class=\"err\">`</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">has</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">2</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"p\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">root</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">asahi</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">linux</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">drivers</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">net</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">phy</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">ax88796b_rust</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">rs</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"mi\">14</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"mi\">1</span>\n<span class=\"w\">   </span><span class=\"o\">|</span>\n<span class=\"mi\">14</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">kernel</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">module_phy_driver</span><span class=\"o\">!</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"mi\">15</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">|</span><span class=\"w\">     </span><span class=\"n\">drivers</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"n\">PhyAX88772A</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">PhyAX88772C</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">PhyAX88796B</span><span class=\"p\">],</span>\n<span class=\"mi\">16</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">|</span><span class=\"w\">     </span><span class=\"n\">device_table</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">[</span>\n<span class=\"mi\">17</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">|</span><span class=\"w\">         </span><span class=\"n\">DeviceId</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">new_with_driver</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">PhyAX88772A</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"p\">(),</span>\n<span class=\"o\">..</span><span class=\"p\">.</